column1: Sums may not equal to totals due to rounding.
(1) Published data reflects State-supplied data without FHWA estimation procedures applied, except where noted.
(2) State did not report government registration data for 1 or more vehicle types.
(3) Data was estimated by FHWA due to data quality concerns which were not addressed by the State per FHWA's request.

(4) State verified significant decreases in reported data due to the instability caused by Covid-19 pandemic; accurate reporting anticipated to resume in 2023. FHWA estimated data due to data quality concerns.
(5) State provided estimated registration data in lieu of actual registration counts.
